 exacting, and its conclusions exciting.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 06. Mrz 2024) 0aDigital media. 0aDiscourse analysis, Narrative. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Anthropology / Cultural & Social.2bisacsh  aage of information.  acultural production.  adigital age.  ainformation technology.  ainformational culture.  ainterpretation.  anarrative.  anew media.  asensation.  atechno-cultural writing.1 aBassett, Caroline, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertManchester University Press 1986 - 2013 eBook Packagez978311128363040uhttps://doi.org/10.7765/978184779161040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781847791610423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781847791610/original  a978-3-11-128363-0  Manchester University Press 1986 - 2013 eBook Packagec1986d2013  aGBV-deGruyter-alles